imdb.plot outline: Going Viral is a Link Court Production that is based on music videos and viral videos on the web. Join hosts George, Krissy, K-Dazzle, and Big Sexy as they bring you the latest videos buzzing on the web, play music videos, go out and talk to random strangers in the community and bring you their own original skits. This is the show where the ultimate goal is not going platinum, but Going Viral.
